ONCE, I TOLD HER

15:09.809 --> 15:11.544
THAT I SAW MY SISTER
KISSING THE, UH--

15:11.644 --> 15:13.446
THE GARDENER
BEHIND THE HOUSE.

15:13.546 --> 15:17.150
SHE WENT BALLISTIC.
SHE NEARLY HAD A CORONARY.

15:17.250 --> 15:19.953
YOU KNOW,
ONCE MARIA HAD
A BLIND DATE,

15:20.053 --> 15:21.354
AND BEFORE HE GOT THERE

