TO OPEN THE DOOR

15:25.158 --> 15:26.526
AND PRETEND THAT I WAS HER.

15:26.626 --> 15:28.328
AND SHE'D WATCH
FROM THE ROOM NEXT DOOR

15:28.428 --> 15:30.397
AND IF SHE DIDN'T LIKE HIM,
SHE JUST WOULDN'T COME OUT

15:30.497 --> 15:34.201
AND I COULD PRETEND THAT
I WAS SICK AND CANCEL THE DATE.

15:34.301 --> 15:37.137
SO WHEN I OPENED THE DOOR,
HE WAS REALLY CUTE.

15:37.237 --> 15:39.906
AND I THOUGHT SHE'D
BE INTERESTED IN HIM.

15:40.007 --> 15:42.075
SO I KEPT TALKING TO HIM

15:42.175 --> 15:44.877
AND PRETENDING TO BE HER
AND CHATTING AWAY.

15:44.978 --> 15:49.782
AND FINALLY, SHE CAME
OUT FROM THE OTHER ROOM
AND SAID, "HI, I'M MARIA."

15:49.882 --> 15:52.352
AND HE WAS
COMPLETELY CONFUSED,

15:52.452 --> 15:55.655
AND I WAS
UTTERLY HUMILIATED.

15:55.755 --> 15:57.624
I-- I WENT SO RED.
ACTUALLY,

15:57.724 --> 15:59.726
