WHEN I THINK ABOUT IT TODAY.

15:59.826 --> 16:02.195
AND SHE TOLD HIM
THAT I WAS

16:02.295 --> 16:03.830
JUST CHECKING OUT
HER DATES FOR HER

16:03.930 --> 16:06.333
AND THAT AT IT WAS
ALL JUST A JOKE.

16:10.103 --> 16:11.671
