WAS TO SEE THE LOOK
OF RELIEF ON HIS FACE

16:19.279 --> 16:21.848
WHEN HE REALIZED THAT
SHE WAS HIS DATE, NOT ME,

16:21.948 --> 16:23.750
THE FATSO.

16:24.884 --> 16:26.553
HILARIOUS, RIGHT?

16:29.789 --> 16:32.559
( sighs )
DON'T WORRY, I GOT BACK
AT HER YEARS LATER.

