TWO DATES ANYWAY."

16:41.968 --> 16:43.370
AND I SAID
"OH, HE TOLD ME

16:43.470 --> 16:46.306
THAT HE DUMPED YOU BECAUSE
YOU SMELLED LIKE TUNA."

16:47.907 --> 16:50.510
- AND IS THAT TRUE?
- NO.

16:50.610 --> 16:53.746
SO REALLY, YOU SETTLED
THAT ACCOUNT IN BED.

16:54.547 --> 16:56.216
I DID INDEED.

17:03.323 --> 17:06.193
