ANOTHER ACCOUNT IN BED,

17:06.293 --> 17:08.027
WITH JAKE THIS TIME.

17:08.128 --> 17:10.797
WHAT, BECAUSE HE'S BECOME
TOO SENSITIVE FOR YOU?

17:22.942 --> 17:26.846
SO-- SO LET ME MAKE SURE
I HAVE THIS RIGHT.

17:26.946 --> 17:28.781
YOUR FATHER DIED
WHEN YOU WERE 13.

17:28.881 --> 17:33.353
- YES.
- YOU MUST HAVE BEEN
PRETTY DEVASTATED.

17:34.754 --> 17:36.289
I WAS.

17:36.389 --> 17:39.326
HE WAS A LOVELY MAN.
HE WAS AFFECTIONATE AND...

17:39.426 --> 17:41.094
GREAT.

17:42.028 --> 17:44.364
PHYSICALLY AFFECTIONATE?

17:48.000 --> 17:49.569
YEAH.

17:51.204 --> 17:52.872
HE'D COME INTO
OUR ROOM AT NIGHT

17:52.972 --> 17:55.041
WHEN WE WERE SLEEPING AND...

17:55.142 --> 17:56.809
KISS US ON THE EYES.

17:58.678 --> 18:02.215
AND THEN I'D HALF WAKE UP,
I'D SMELL HIS AFTERSHAVE

18:02.315 --> 18:04.884
AND KNOW THAT HE WAS THERE.

18:04.984 --> 18:07.854
AND THEN HE'D
WHISPER IN MY EAR
THAT HE LOVED ME AND...

18:09.489 --> 18:11.824
HE'D HOLD MY FACE
IN HIS HANDS.

18:11.924 --> 18:15.162
HE HAD THESE HUGE HANDS,
LIKE A CONSTRUCTION WORKER.

18:17.797 --> 18:19.232
AND HE WAS JUST...

18:19.332 --> 18:23.436
