IT WAS DISGUSTING.

18:45.592 --> 18:48.161
DO YOU THINK THAT MIGHT BE
BECAUSE IT SCARES YOU?

18:48.261 --> 18:49.996
THAT YOU'VE LEARNED
YOU CAN'T TRUST PEOPLE

18:50.096 --> 18:52.265
WHO EXPRESS
THEMSELVES TENDERLY,

18:52.365 --> 18:55.668
