18:55.768 --> 18:59.339
THAT THEY'RE GOING
TO ABANDON YOU, DIE
AND LEAVE YOU BEHIND?

18:59.439 --> 19:01.040
AND SO IN ORDER
TO AVOID THAT,

19:01.140 --> 19:02.942
YOU PROVOKE JAKE.
YOU MAKE HIM ANGRY.

19:03.042 --> 19:06.746
