BE THAT BAD.

19:40.380 --> 19:42.249
BUT YOU'LL EXPLAIN IT
TO JAKE IF HE FINDS OUT.

19:42.349 --> 19:44.317
CAN YOU--
CAN YOU MAKE SENSE
OF IT FOR HIM?

19:44.417 --> 19:46.686
