THAT YOU WANT ME TO TELL HIM?

19:46.786 --> 19:48.488
THAT I'M FUCKED UP.

19:48.588 --> 19:50.690
THAT I CAN'T HELP MYSELF.
THAT-- THAT IT'S BIGGER THAN ME.

19:50.790 --> 19:52.459
JUST TELL HIM
THAT I'M FUCKED UP.

19:52.559 --> 19:54.193
BUT EVEN IF
JAKE FORGIVES YOU,

19:54.294 --> 19:57.697
DO YOU THINK THAT YOU
CAN FORGIVE YOURSELF?

19:57.797 --> 19:59.666
I ALWAYS FORGIVE MYSELF.

19:59.766 --> 20:03.102
THAT'S MY PROBLEM.
I-- I JUST CLOSE MY EYES

20:03.202 --> 20:04.871
BEFORE I GO
TO SLEEP AT NIGHT

20:04.971 --> 20:06.138
AND I ASK GOD
FOR FORGIVENESS

20:06.239 --> 20:08.308
AND I FORGIVE MYSELF
FOR EVERYTHING.

20:13.112 --> 20:15.748
